@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gunokh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (tmp - wp.cos(wp.sin(tmp + 0.85)))
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.49 * v0 + 0.89) * v0) - (v2 * (tmp + 0.38 * v0 + 0.20)))
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.cos(tmp + 0.75)) - ((v1 + 0.31 * v1 + 0.92) + (v2 + 0.40 - v2 + 0.35)))
    v0 = (0.55 + 0.75)
    tmp = wp.exp(0.17)
    v0 = wp.exp(0.74)
    v2 = tmp
    v1 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
